data.description: MLS# 270029 Welcome to this stunning single-level home offering the perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this spacious residence spans 2,125 sq. ft. and features a 3-car garage for ample parking and storage. Step inside to discover a beautifully updated interior, with LPV floors that are scratch and stain resistant, and freshly painted walls throughout. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring gas cooking and top-of-the-line LG appliances purchased in 2020, including a stove, microwave, dishwasher, and French door refrigerator. A cozy fireplace enhances the inviting living area, creating a warm ambiance for relaxation and gatherings. Enjoy the convenience of a gas dryer and washer, both included with the home. The AC was replaced in 2020, ensuring year-round comfort, while a whole house water softener provides added luxury. Solar panels were installed in 2021, dramatically reducing energy costs. If connected to the grid, your total electric bill can be as low as $21. Outside, a nicely sized yard with underground sprinklers offers a tranquil space for outdoor activities. The lot spans 10,088 sq. ft., providing ample room for outdoor enjoyment. With an annual HOA fee of $150, this property is located within the sought-after Kamiakin HS, Desert Hills Middle School, and Amon Creek Elementary district (Buyer to confirm). Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional home your own, offering modern upgrades and an ideal location for a comfortable and convenient lifestyle. For more detail, check out the photography, video, floor plan.
